text-align:center;width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;display:block;background:transparent"><div style="width:300px;height:250px;margin:auto;overflow:hidden;position:relative;background:rgba(71, 73, 103, 0.10);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px #28293D"><div class="MuiBox-root css-1dm7ec5" id="div-gpt-ad-1731941770755-0" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;z-index:1"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_roundedCornersContainer__D5D_p"><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY gameDescription_first" style="margin-block-end:1em"><p>Fashion Store: Shop Tycoon is a casual tycoon game where you manage your own boutique clothes store. Craft your store layout, attract customers, and maximize profits to expand your fashion empire. Are you ready to become the ultimate fashion tycoon?</div><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY">
<h2>How to Play</h2>
<h3>Start your retail business</h3>
<p>Set up your first clothes stand to get your first batch of stock. Once it’s set up, your customers will start rolling in, and you can collect their cash at the cash register!</p>
<h3>Expand your premises</h3>
<p>Using the money from your paying customers, you can add more clothes stands and expand the retail space to fit more stock for customers to browse. As the customer flow increases, so does the need for assistance. At the upgrade bench, you can hire more shop assistants and upgrade their abilities. </p>
<h3>Upgrade your abilites</h3>
<p>There’s a whole host of options to improve the operation of your fashion store at the upgrade bench. You can increase your carrying capacity and charge speed. Customers can be upgraded too, offering more money and tips to help you grow your fashion store tycoon.</p>
<h3>Move to the next store</h3>
<p>As you progress, you’ll find new ways to make money, like selling clothes online. This generates a nice bit of passive income while you run the shop! Eventually, you can buy another store and move to level 2, where you sell new items to higher paying clientele!</p>
<h2>More Games Like This</h2>
<p>There are more <a target="_blank" href="https://www.crazygames.com/c/casual">casual games</a> to play on CrazyGames once you’ve finished playing Fashion Store: Shop Tycoon. You can play a simple but addictive game like <a target="_blank" href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/tiny-fishing">Tiny Fishing</a> or hop into another fun sim like this in <a target="_blank" href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/create-your-beach">Create Your Beach</a>.</p>
